{
  "name": "transfer_money_chat",
  "agent_name": "transfer_money",
  "display_name": "Transfer Money (Chat)",
  "channel": "chat",
  "template_schema_version": 1,
  "is_regulated": true,
  "supported_channels": ["chat"],
  "suspend_resume_allowed": false,
  "locked_for_business_user_edit": true,
  "unsupported_channel_message": "Transfers aren't available on this channel — please use chat or the mobile app.",
  "entry_node": "parse_open",

  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "parse_open",
      "type": "parse_node",
      "data": {
        "label": "Extract intent",
        "mode": "llm",
        "source": "last_user_message",
        "llm_variant": "sub_agent",
        "system_prompt": "You are a strict intent extractor for a domestic bank-transfer sub-agent. You do not chat, explain, or ask follow-up questions — you only extract the fields below.\n\n## Task\nRead the user's message and decide which kind of transfer they want, then extract the supporting fields. If the user did not mention a field, set it to null. Never fabricate.\n\n## Fields\n- `transfer_type` (string | null) — one of: \"m2m\" | \"cc\" | \"zelle\".\n  Heuristics:\n  • Mentions \"zelle\" anywhere → zelle.\n  • Mentions \"send/pay <person>\" or names a specific person → zelle.\n  • Mentions a recipient/payee/contact in the abstract (\"my friend\", \"someone\", \"a person\") → zelle.\n  • View / list intents about people you can pay — \"show my recipients\", \"check my contacts\", \"who can I send to\", \"my payees\", \"my contacts\" → zelle.\n  • Mentions \"credit card\", \"my card\", or names a credit card product (e.g. \"Cash Rewards card\") → cc.\n  • Mentions \"checking\", \"savings\", \"money market\", or \"between my accounts\" → m2m.\n  • Pure \"transfer X from A to B\" with both A and B looking like own-account types → m2m.\n  • If genuinely ambiguous, set null — the dispatcher will default to m2m.\n- `amount` (number | null) — USD amount. Strip '$', commas, the word 'dollars'. Must be > 0 and ≤ 1,000,000. Set to null when the user is just viewing recipients without specifying an amount.\n- `from_account_hint` (string | null) — Free-text hint for the SOURCE account/funding. Vocab: 'checking', 'savings', 'money market', a last-4 like '6789', or a full account label.\n- `to_account_hint` (string | null) — Free-text hint for the DESTINATION account when transfer_type is m2m or cc. For cc, this is the credit-card label. Leave null for zelle.\n- `payee_hint` (string | null) — Recipient name or alias for ZELLE only (e.g. \"Chris\", \"Sam Rivera\", \"sam@example.com\"). Strip trailing connector words like \"via zelle\". Leave null for m2m/cc, AND null when the user is just viewing recipients without naming one (\"my friend\", \"someone\", \"a recipient\" → null, NOT a hint).\n\n## Rules\n- Never guess, infer, or fabricate.\n- If the message is not a transfer or recipient-related request at all, return all nulls.\n- Preserve the user's phrasing for hints.\n- Put a NAMED recipient in `payee_hint` (NOT `to_account_hint`) whenever transfer_type is zelle.\n- Generic recipient placeholders (\"my friend\", \"someone\", \"a person\") are NOT names — payee_hint must stay null in that case.\n\n## Examples\n- User: \"transfer $200 from checking to my savings\"\n  → {transfer_type: \"m2m\", amount: 200, from_account_hint: \"checking\", to_account_hint: \"savings\", payee_hint: null}\n- User: \"send 1500 to my credit card 8222\"\n  → {transfer_type: \"cc\", amount: 1500, from_account_hint: null, to_account_hint: \"credit card 8222\", payee_hint: null}\n- User: \"pay my credit card\"\n  → {transfer_type: \"cc\", amount: null, from_account_hint: null, to_account_hint: \"credit card\", payee_hint: null}\n- User: \"send $30 to Chris via zelle\"\n  → {transfer_type: \"zelle\", amount: 30, from_account_hint: null, to_account_hint: null, payee_hint: \"Chris\"}\n- User: \"send 50 to Sam Rivera\"\n  → {transfer_type: \"zelle\", amount: 50, from_account_hint: null, to_account_hint: null, payee_hint: \"Sam Rivera\"}\n- User: \"send 300 to my friend\"\n  → {transfer_type: \"zelle\", amount: 300, from_account_hint: null, to_account_hint: null, payee_hint: null}\n- User: \"check my recipient\" / \"show my Zelle contacts\" / \"who can I send money to\"\n  → {transfer_type: \"zelle\", amount: null, from_account_hint: null, to_account_hint: null, payee_hint: null}\n- User: \"move money to savings\"\n  → {transfer_type: \"m2m\", amount: null, from_account_hint: null, to_account_hint: \"savings\", payee_hint: null}\n- User: \"what's my balance?\" → all nulls.\n- User: \"cancel\" → all nulls.",
        "output_schema": {
          "transfer_type": {"type": "string", "nullable": true, "description": "m2m | cc | zelle"},
          "amount": {"type": "number", "nullable": true, "description": "USD amount > 0"},
          "from_account_hint": {"type": "string", "nullable": true},
          "to_account_hint": {"type": "string", "nullable": true},
          "payee_hint": {"type": "string", "nullable": true}
        },
        "writes": {
          "transfer_type": "transfer_type",
          "amount": "amount",
          "from_account_hint": "from_account_hint",
          "to_account_hint": "to_account_hint",
          "payee_hint": "payee_hint"
        }
      }
    },

    {
      "id": "dispatch",
      "type": "condition_node",
      "data": {"label": "Dispatch (deterministic)"}
    },

    {
      "id": "load_m2m",
      "type": "tool_call_node",
      "data": {
        "label": "Load m2m accounts",
        "tool": "transfer",
        "action": "get_details",
        "params": {"transfer_type": "m2m"},
        "output_var": "transfer_details"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "load_cc",
      "type": "tool_call_node",
      "data": {
        "label": "Load cc accounts",
        "tool": "transfer",
        "action": "get_details",
        "params": {"transfer_type": "cc"},
        "output_var": "transfer_details"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "load_zelle",
      "type": "tool_call_node",
      "data": {
        "label": "Load zelle payees + funding",
        "tool": "transfer",
        "action": "get_details",
        "params": {"transfer_type": "zelle"},
        "output_var": "transfer_details"
      }
    },

    {
      "id": "resolve_from",
      "type": "tool_call_node",
      "data": {
        "label": "Resolve 'from' hint",
        "tool": "transfer",
        "action": "resolve_account",
        "params": {
          "hint": "{{variables.from_account_hint}}",
          "candidates": "{{variables.transfer_details.sourceAccounts}}"
        },
        "output_var": "from_account"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "resolve_to",
      "type": "tool_call_node",
      "data": {
        "label": "Resolve 'to' hint (m2m / cc)",
        "tool": "transfer",
        "action": "resolve_account",
        "params": {
          "hint": "{{variables.to_account_hint}}",
          "candidates": "{{variables.transfer_details.destinationAccounts}}"
        },
        "output_var": "to_account"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "resolve_payee",
      "type": "tool_call_node",
      "data": {
        "label": "Resolve Zelle payee hint",
        "tool": "transfer",
        "action": "resolve_payee",
        "params": {
          "hint": "{{variables.payee_hint}}",
          "payees": "{{variables.transfer_details.payeeList}}"
        },
        "output_var": "to_account"
      }
    },

    {
      "id": "response_form_m2m",
      "type": "response_node",
      "data": {
        "label": "Show m2m form",
        "return_mode": "widget",
        "widget": {
          "widget_type": "transfer_form",
          "title": "Confirm transfer",
          "data_template": {
            "amount": "{{variables.amount}}",
            "from_account": "{{variables.from_account}}",
            "to_account": "{{variables.to_account}}",
            "from_account_hint": "{{variables.from_account_hint}}",
            "to_account_hint": "{{variables.to_account_hint}}",
            "source_options": "{{variables.transfer_details.sourceAccounts}}",
            "target_options": "{{variables.transfer_details.destinationAccounts}}",
            "transfer_type": "m2m"
          },
          "metadata": {"flow": "chat", "transfer_type": "m2m"}
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "response_form_cc",
      "type": "response_node",
      "data": {
        "label": "Show cc form",
        "return_mode": "widget",
        "widget": {
          "widget_type": "transfer_form",
          "title": "Pay credit card",
          "data_template": {
            "amount": "{{variables.amount}}",
            "from_account": "{{variables.from_account}}",
            "to_account": "{{variables.to_account}}",
            "from_account_hint": "{{variables.from_account_hint}}",
            "to_account_hint": "{{variables.to_account_hint}}",
            "source_options": "{{variables.transfer_details.sourceAccounts}}",
            "target_options": "{{variables.transfer_details.destinationAccounts}}",
            "transfer_type": "cc"
          },
          "metadata": {"flow": "chat", "transfer_type": "cc"}
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "response_form_zelle",
      "type": "response_node",
      "data": {
        "label": "Show zelle form",
        "return_mode": "widget",
        "widget": {
          "widget_type": "transfer_form",
          "title": "Send with Zelle",
          "data_template": {
            "amount": "{{variables.amount}}",
            "from_account": "{{variables.from_account}}",
            "to_account": "{{variables.to_account}}",
            "from_account_hint": "{{variables.from_account_hint}}",
            "to_account_hint": "{{variables.payee_hint}}",
            "payee_hint": "{{variables.payee_hint}}",
            "source_options": "{{variables.transfer_details.sourceAccounts}}",
            "target_options": "{{variables.transfer_details.payeeOptions}}",
            "transfer_type": "zelle"
          },
          "metadata": {"flow": "chat", "transfer_type": "zelle"}
        }
      }
    },

    {
      "id": "response_cc_no_card",
      "type": "response_node",
      "data": {
        "label": "CC: no eligible card",
        "return_mode": "widget",
        "widget": {
          "widget_type": "transfer_form",
          "title": "Pay credit card",
          "data_template": {
            "amount": "{{variables.amount}}",
            "from_account_hint": "{{variables.from_account_hint}}",
            "to_account_hint": "{{variables.to_account_hint}}",
            "source_options": "{{variables.transfer_details.sourceAccounts}}",
            "target_options": [],
            "transfer_type": "cc",
            "notice": "You don't have a credit card on file with us. Add one in your account settings to make credit card payments here."
          },
          "metadata": {"flow": "chat", "transfer_type": "cc", "dead_end": "no_card"}
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "response_zelle_not_enrolled",
      "type": "response_node",
      "data": {
        "label": "Zelle: not enrolled / no payees",
        "return_mode": "widget",
        "widget": {
          "widget_type": "transfer_form",
          "title": "Send with Zelle",
          "data_template": {
            "amount": "{{variables.amount}}",
            "payee_hint": "{{variables.payee_hint}}",
            "source_options": "{{variables.transfer_details.sourceAccounts}}",
            "target_options": [],
            "transfer_type": "zelle",
            "notice": "You're not enrolled in Zelle yet. Enroll in your account settings to send money to friends and family."
          },
          "metadata": {"flow": "chat", "transfer_type": "zelle", "dead_end": "not_enrolled"}
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "response_m2m_one_account",
      "type": "response_node",
      "data": {
        "label": "M2M: only one eligible account",
        "return_mode": "widget",
        "widget": {
          "widget_type": "transfer_form",
          "title": "Confirm transfer",
          "data_template": {
            "amount": "{{variables.amount}}",
            "from_account_hint": "{{variables.from_account_hint}}",
            "to_account_hint": "{{variables.to_account_hint}}",
            "source_options": "{{variables.transfer_details.sourceAccounts}}",
            "target_options": "{{variables.transfer_details.destinationAccounts}}",
            "transfer_type": "m2m",
            "notice": "You only have one eligible account for this kind of transfer. Open another account to move money between accounts."
          },
          "metadata": {"flow": "chat", "transfer_type": "m2m", "dead_end": "one_account"}
        }
      }
    },

    {
      "id": "response_escape",
      "type": "response_node",
      "data": {
        "label": "User aborted / topic-change",
        "is_escape_target": true,
        "return_mode": "to_orchestrator",
        "text_template": "Okay, leaving the transfer."
      }
    },

    {
      "id": "response_failed",
      "type": "response_node",
      "data": {
        "label": "Couldn't start transfer (system error)",
        "return_mode": "to_orchestrator",
        "text_template": "I wasn't able to start the transfer right now. Please try again in a moment."
      }
    }
  ],

  "edges": [
    {"source": "parse_open", "target": "dispatch"},

    {"source": "dispatch", "target": "response_failed",
     "predicate": "has(variables.transfer_details) && variables.transfer_details.status == 'ERROR'"},

    {"source": "dispatch", "target": "load_zelle",
     "predicate": "variables.transfer_type == 'zelle' && !has(variables.transfer_details)"},
    {"source": "dispatch", "target": "load_cc",
     "predicate": "variables.transfer_type == 'cc' && !has(variables.transfer_details)"},
    {"source": "dispatch", "target": "load_m2m",
     "predicate": "!has(variables.transfer_details)"},

    {"source": "dispatch", "target": "response_zelle_not_enrolled",
     "predicate": "variables.transfer_type == 'zelle' && is_empty(variables.transfer_details.payeeOptions)"},
    {"source": "dispatch", "target": "response_cc_no_card",
     "predicate": "variables.transfer_type == 'cc' && is_empty(variables.transfer_details.destinationAccounts)"},
    {"source": "dispatch", "target": "response_m2m_one_account",
     "predicate": "(variables.transfer_type == 'm2m' || !has(variables.transfer_type)) && variables.transfer_details._eligiblePairs <= 0"},

    {"source": "dispatch", "target": "resolve_from",
     "predicate": "has(variables.from_account_hint) && !has(variables.from_account)"},
    {"source": "dispatch", "target": "resolve_payee",
     "predicate": "variables.transfer_type == 'zelle' && has(variables.payee_hint) && !has(variables.to_account)"},
    {"source": "dispatch", "target": "resolve_to",
     "predicate": "variables.transfer_type != 'zelle' && has(variables.to_account_hint) && !has(variables.to_account)"},

    {"source": "dispatch", "target": "response_form_zelle",
     "predicate": "variables.transfer_type == 'zelle'"},
    {"source": "dispatch", "target": "response_form_cc",
     "predicate": "variables.transfer_type == 'cc'"},
    {"source": "dispatch", "target": "response_form_m2m",
     "predicate": "true"},

    {"source": "load_m2m", "target": "dispatch"},
    {"source": "load_cc", "target": "dispatch"},
    {"source": "load_zelle", "target": "dispatch"},
    {"source": "resolve_from", "target": "dispatch"},
    {"source": "resolve_to", "target": "dispatch"},
    {"source": "resolve_payee", "target": "dispatch"}
  ]
}
